  "texts": [
    "This section outlines three interventions of ChatGPT integration, each applied in separate practice sessions.",
    "The initial intervention was conducted in the first practice session in the fourth week of the semester.",
    "In this session, students were given the task of developing a Python program to compute the area of a triangle and a rectangle.",
    "The targeted topics were variables and functions.",
    "The intervention allowed students to use ChatGPT for seeking help without any restrictions or guidance."
  ]
}